<note n="0745015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0745015">Yama.</note>
<note n="0745016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0745016">王＝天【和】</note>
<note n="0745017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0745017">〔主〕－【明】【和】</note>
<note n="0745018" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0745018">〔場〕－【和】</note>
<note n="0745019" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0745019">成熟＝成就【明】【和】</note>
</p>
